::Prowl/Striker/Kluster::

Prowl looks at Tygerhawk, a bit confused. "What's this about Iron Rapt-AAHH!!"

He nearly falls out of the air as he goes half transparent.

"All Maximals," he says over his comm-link, "I'll be gone for a few days. 
Tygerhawk is back, so I guess he's in charge."

He switches his comm-link to transmit to Lunarpine. "I picked up some strange 
transmission. It said where a Maximal was. Maybe its Shadow Wing," he says, 
his comm-link sending the coordinates before he phases out.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
In a hallway of the Cybertronian Fire, Striker nearly falls against the wall, 
feeling himself lose energy. He growls. He was gonna be gone for a while. 
Before he could send a comm, he phases out.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster slumps back into his chair, going half-transparent.

"Chordate, you're in charge untill I phase back in," he says, phasing out.
